description: This file appears to be a configuration include file for setting up build environment variables and tuning options specific to the 'aarch64' (ARM 64-bit) architecture within a Yocto Project layer. It defines tuning features, package architectures, and related configurations for 'aarch64' and 'aarch64_be' endianness.

methods.name: bb.utils.contains
methods.description: Checks if a specific feature or string is present within a variable.

methods.name: bb.utils.getVar
methods.description: Retrieves the value of a variable in the build environment.
